Customization of i3bar blocks

status_command launch a program to be displayed on the bar (text output)

i3blocks is better. Install it

Customize it: /etc/i3blocks.conf (option -c to specify new conf file location)

Fix audio volume problems:
1. install pavucontrol
2. change the script volume to command=/usr/share/i3blocks/volume 5 pulse
3. change interval to 1
